{"tid":1589502,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［創意升級方向］抗爭融入生活 10點鳩叫都要升級","createTime":"2019-09-23T10:17:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T08:44:09.000Z","uid":90306,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"76fff048beacfce48f59f689e4cc88bd949bc5ec","tid":1589502,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:17:51.000Z","msg":"最近聽到好多巴絲都話抗爭已經融入生活唔會完，然後又見到兩位巴打嘅post<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><pre><code data-type=\"\">忽發奇想 點解平時唔會係黨鐵入面鳩叫？？？\nhttps://lih.kg/1581587\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區\n\n[集思廣益] [ 幫手推] 全新文宣x鳩叫!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\nhttps://lih.kg/1589198\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</code></pre></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">返工望住黨鐵站巴士站都咁多人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>不如就試下<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">等車轉車</span>個陣鳩叫啦</ins></strong></span></span></div><br />\n<strong><ins>地點</ins></strong>：<span style=\"color: red;\">最緊要多人就會有人和應！</span>中環、金鐘、北角、九龍塘、油塘，總之各大黨鐵站內；紅隧口、各大巴士總站、甚至只係你街頭街尾一個多人啲嘅巴士站。<br />\n<strong><ins>時間</ins></strong>：<span style=\"color: red;\">返工返學放工繁忙時間</span>，只要見到多人就鳩叫，總有手足會和應！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><ins>每日都叫口號，真正令抗爭融入生活<br />\n隨時隨地抗爭狀態</ins></div></span><br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉，歡迎討論，最後：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"fdda561813edff8308d5e3b03cdfb587e7a744f3","tid":1589502,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:18:22.000Z","msg":"自推10連<br />\n1/1"},{"pid":"5e0c94829dc4644727bc17e8adb708a7a6174df4","tid":1589502,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:18:23.000Z","msg":"[緊急][公投][置頂] 10.1集合定分區搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589182</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c3337bba989c793007f